Subject: drm/rockchip: Use fbdev-dma
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b4c3fe533cd1afeac057ef1e79358d3b36f184f8
